com.satori.rtm.model

Class SubscriptionData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.satori.rtm.model.SubscriptionData

  • public class SubscriptionData
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the body value of a PDU for a subscription data.

    Subscription data PDUs contain messages published to a subscribed channel. If the subscription uses a streamview, the messages may be filtered and transformed. A single SubscriptionData can contain multiple messages.

    Subscription data PDUs have the following structure: 

     {
     "action": "rtm/subscription/data",
     "body": {
         "position":Position,
         "messages":[Message],
         "subscription_id":SubscriptionId
     }
 }
